### Introduction

On May 22 and 23, 2026, the scenic municipality of **Benahavís in Málaga, Spain**, played host to a high-profile corporate gathering requiring premier event production. Partnering with the prominent agency **Bmotion**, **Malaga Event Gear (MEG)** stepped in as the trusted technical partner to manage the complete corporate event AV solutions.

Leveraging decades of experience and top-tier technology, the **MEG** team guaranteed an ultra-professional, seamless execution that captivated attendees and smoothly delivered the client’s vision.

![](https://cdn.malagaeventgear.com/blog/3093/2026.05.22-23-Bmotion-Benahavis-1-576x1024.webp)

![](https://cdn.malagaeventgear.com/blog/3092/2026.05.22-23-Bmotion-Benahavis-0-1024x576.webp)

### Event Overview

[Bmotion](https://www.bmotionav.com/), a leader in high-impact event design and production, required a reliable local partner capable of transforming a premium venue in the Benahavís area into a fully functional, high-tech corporate stage. **Benahavís**, renowned for its luxury resorts and stunning landscapes on the **Costa del Sol**, demands an elite standard of service for international and domestic business clients alike.

Given the complex needs of modern corporate conferences, the technical setup had to accommodate dynamic multimedia presentations, crystal-clear speech reinforcement, and sharp visual displays to engage a discerning corporate audience over the multi-day event.

### MEG’s Role

To meet **Bmotion’s** exact standards, **Malaga Event Gear** deployed a comprehensive audiovisual equipment rental Málaga [package](/packages/) tailored specifically for executive meetings and corporate presentations. Understanding that flawless communication is the backbone of any successful **MICE** event, **MEG** assumed complete responsibility for the logistics, technical design, on-site installation, and live operations.

Since all services offered by **MEG** are delivered entirely in native-level English, collaboration with the international crew and organizers was fluid, eliminating any potential language barriers and allowing the event schedule to progress exactly on time.

### Technical Highlights

The technical framework utilized state-of-the-art visual and sound infrastructure to provide an immersive environment. For the visual showcase, high-resolution display screens paired with a high-performance 5000-lumen presentation projector were installed to maintain bright, razor-sharp imagery even under ambient corporate lighting.

On the audio front, a premium sound system with balanced column array speakers and subwoofers provided uniform, crystal-clear audio coverage across the entire seating area. Presenters were equipped with a mix of flexible gooseneck microphones mounted on a sleek methacrylate lectern for formal addresses, alongside premium wireless microphones that allowed effortless movement during interactive panels and Q&A sessions.

The primary technical challenge involved managing the venue’s natural acoustics and lighting variables over a two-day schedule. **MEG’s** dedicated on-site technicians monitored the sound frequencies and video inputs continuously from an advanced control panel, ensuring zero latency, seamless input switching, and flawless performance from the first opening remark to the closing applause.

### Impact and Outcome

The collaboration between **Bmotion** and **Malaga Event Gear** resulted in an impeccably executed corporate event. Speakers delivered their insights with total confidence, backed by robust technology that left no room for glitches.

The crisp visuals and immaculate audio production kept the audience engaged throughout the dense presentation schedules, reinforcing **Bmotion’s** reputation for excellence and highlighting **MEG’s** position as a premier provider of lighting and sound services in Spain.

### Professional AV Solutions on the Costa del Sol

Since 1996, **Malaga Event Gear** has been elevating corporate meetings, conferences, and private celebrations across the region, building a proud track record of over 1,000 satisfied clients.

By blending high-quality equipment with a highly trained, English-speaking technical team, **MEG** handles the stress of technical execution so brands can focus entirely on their message.

